 principal interest is in the effect of health information 
 on prices, orthogonalised sudden desires are adopted here 
 given that in the current application changes in the 
 food (being talked about a lot on TV, online, etc.) index are likely to drive price changes 
 and not the other way around, too. Given that prices at all stages of 
